long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Tools for Autodarts enhances the gaming experience on https://autodarts.io/ with features like color customization, auto-start games once a player joined, discord webhooks and TV like streamer mode.

Note: This is not an official extension of the Autodarts team and is no more than a hobby project which is powered by autodarts.io
